BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:7yl2uVtlFY2TYZzfoTVwq
SUMMARY:RS 101: Intro to Vera's Recording Studio
DTSTAMP:20260327T071013Z
DTSTART:20260425T200000Z
DESCRIPTION:Get into VERA’s Recording Studio through this 2-hour workshop a
	nd studio orientation! Learn the studio infrastructure including\, bootup\
	, signalflow\, patchbay setup\, mixing desk operation\, and basic Digital 
	Audio Workstation (DAW) integration. During this session\, participants wi
	ll experiment with different ways of running signals from the live room to
	 the computer. Some familiarity with Digital Audio Workstations (i.e. ProT
	ools\, Logic\, Reaper\, Ableton\, etc.) is encouraged.\n\nAfter taking thi
	s course\, students who are new to studio recording should be ready for th
	e multi-week Recording Studio Workshop Series\, as well as having a better
	 grounding for independent research. Students who are experienced with stu
	dio recording may be credentialed for volunteering at studio sessions.\n\n
	https://link.dice.fm/tebc13c0eb8b\n\nFrom The Vera Project
